OL,3,CCancer patient told he was 'deceased'
OL,4,Cby doctor's surgery
OL,6,FA man from Hampshire who was told he
OL,7,Fwas dead says the effect has been
OL,8,Fdevastating to his mental health.JJohn
OL,9,FAshcroft, who is 74 and from
OL,10,FPortsmouth is undergoing treatment for
OL,11,Fprostate cancer.
OL,13,FHe received a phonecall from his
OL,14,FDoctor's surgery saying their system
OL,15,Fshowed him as "deceased."
OL,17,FThis meant all his medical records and
OL,18,Fappointments had vanished and he has
OL,19,Fbeen unable to reorder his medication.
