OL,6,FTwo weeks on and with the help of his
OL,7,Fwife Susan, John is now officially
OL,8,Falive again at his GP practice.
OL,10,FThe couple still don't know how the
OL,11,Fblunder happened or whether he has
OL,12,Fflagged up as deceased in any other
OL,13,Forganisations.
OL,15,FJohn Ashcroft said: "The phone rang,
OL,16,Fthe person on the other end said it's
OL,17,Fbeen reported you're deceased, but
OL,18,Fquite obviously you're not
