OL,3,CCancer patient told he was 'deceased'
OL,4,Cby doctor's surgery
OL,6,F"It was terribly unnerving, it would
OL,7,Fbe for anybody wouldn't it, to be told
OL,8,Fthey're dead"
OL,10,FJohn's wife, Susan Ashcroft added:
OL,11,F"You can hear someone saying your
OL,12,Fhusband's deceased, but you're sitting
OL,13,Fthere watching him breathing.
OL,15,F"I think what upset me more than
OL,16,Fanything was how it was affecting
OL,17,FJohn, He's in remission from cancer,
OL,18,Fso he has an appointment every 12
OL,19,Fweeks and that appointment was
OL,20,Fcancelled."
