OL,4,Cby doctor's surgery
OL,6,FAn NHS spokesperson said: "We are
OL,7,Faware of an issue involving a civil
OL,8,Fdeath registration being incorrectly
OL,9,Frecorded against a patient's medical
OL,10,Frecord.
OL,12,F"This was removed within three hours
OL,13,Fof it being reported to us and the
OL,14,Fpatient was re-registered by their GP.
OL,16,F"We send our apologies to the patient
OL,17,Finvolved and would encourage him to
OL,18,Fcontact us directly so we can explain
OL,19,Ffurther."
